Titolo: Kaiser Knuckle

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Kaiser Knuckle (カイザーナックル), which is known outside of Japan as Global Champion, is a 1994 fighting game released for the arcades by Taito. Kaiser Knuckle was released during the fighting game trend of the 1990s that began with Capcom's Street Fighter II. It is planned to be included as part of the Taito Egret II mini console, marking its first re-release outside arcades.